The Undersigned hereby declares and represents that the injuries sustained in the
hereinabove described incident or events are or may be permanent and progressive, and
that recovery is uncertain and indefinite, and it is understood and agreed that in making
this release the Undersigned relies wholly upon the Undersigned's judgment, belief and
knowledge of the nature, extent, effect and duration of the injuries and liability therefor,
and that said release is made without reliance upon any statement or representation
made by the party or parties hereby released, by their agents or representatives, or by
any physician or surgeon employed by them.
In further consideration of the aforesaid payment, the Undersigned hereby
warrants that the Undersigned is the sole owner of the aforesaid claims, demands and
causes of action, and does hereby agree and undertake to indemnify and save entirely
harmless the party or parties hereby released from any and all claims, demands, liens or
suits, including the expenses of defending against the same, which may hereafter be
